00:24:42,663 --> 00:24:44,563
Petunjuk Conan Selanjutnya:

429
00:24:44,563 --> 00:24:46,263
"Sushi."

430
00:24:46,263 --> 00:24:47,663
Silahkan pesan sesukanya.

431
00:24:47,663 --> 00:24:50,263
Baiklah! Tuna, tuna sedang dan tuna berlemak.

